  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/2acb42fdba8d4c389bd87bef39ac5bab.avif?t=1728316364\" width=574 height=121 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Holidays are over but the fun is not!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grab your stuff and let's enjoy a new SQUARE WORD episode!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/5ab469a636d5e2446f9bac43496ec081.webp?t=1728316364\" width=600 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MALI, the playful tiger,</strong> can't wait to play with you in this new edition!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/1f537d20c21fed63253f3acea7854c83.webp?t=1728316364\" width=13 height=13 /></span> <strong>Four very cool themes: Sports - Jobs - Places - Autumn</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/1f537d20c21fed63253f3acea7854c83.webp?t=1728316364\" width=13 height=13 /></span> 140+ words to find.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/1f537d20c21fed63253f3acea7854c83.webp?t=1728316364\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Handcrafted grids.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/1f537d20c21fed63253f3acea7854c83.webp?t=1728316364\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Daily challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/1f537d20c21fed63253f3acea7854c83.webp?t=1728316364\" width=13 height=13 /></span> 4 difficulties (easy to very hard).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/1f537d20c21fed63253f3acea7854c83.webp?t=1728316364\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Difficulty increasing gradually.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/1f537d20c21fed63253f3acea7854c83.webp?t=1728316364\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Letter & word hints.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/1f537d20c21fed63253f3acea7854c83.webp?t=1728316364\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Collect Stamps with extra objectives and receive rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/1f537d20c21fed63253f3acea7854c83.webp?t=1728316364\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Additional songs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/251d35a8804c4502b4e4835664bbf141.avif?t=1728316364\" width=616 height=142 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521940/extras/5ab469a636d5e2446f9bac43496ec081.webp?t=1728316364\" width=600 height=5 /></span></p>",
